3
00:00:09,635 --> 00:00:14,396
He was talented, well-organized, and incredibly intelligent.

4
00:00:14,776 --> 00:00:18,357
He committed the perfect crime, then mocked authorities.

5
00:00:18,937 --> 00:00:20,597
It's hard to describe the arrogance.

6
00:00:20,938 --> 00:00:23,138
He just figured he was untouchable.

7
00:00:23,678 --> 00:00:27,119
Find out how he did it, next on Masterminds.

8
00:00:46,107 --> 00:00:47,488
Nobody should die that way.

9
